
AmbientWeather: Glanceable weather information to prepare you for the day

This is a simple, native weather app for BlackBerry 10, made with Cascades.
It uses OpenWeatherMap to pull the weather data and Flickr for the local
images.

Author: Dirk Songuer
Contact: dirk@songuer.de
Link: https://github.com/DirkSonguer/AmbientWeather

Tested with BlackBerry 10.1 on a Z10 and simulator 10.1.0.4828
